  - guid: 50ce82b7-b852-42d5-9ba6-bc61401b4f45
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Queen
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'Good job. A good worker always confirms their task.

        The
        first rule we have here is: Do as I say.

        Repeat with me. Do as I
        say.'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Queen
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'So onto what you are here for.

        We want
        profits. How wo we get profits?

        By milking this poor sucker here.

        <event:enablePhoneView>

        That''s
        your player.'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: 
      <Content>k__BackingField: 'See him clicking away his time?

        See him
        throwing away his allowance for dopamine kicks?

        We want more of
        that. '
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Queen
      <Content>k__BackingField: "How do you do that? You fight. \nBeat up this big
        beefy villain for your player.\nFight well and get him invested in you.\nSee
        his view of you? That's you now. Small, cute, helpless.\n"
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Queen
      <Content>k__BackingField: "That's how you strike. Slip up \"accidentally\"
        \nand land in a disfavourable position during your fights.\nThen scream for
        help. "
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Queen
      <Content>k__BackingField: '<event:moveDialogueBoxUp>

        See that notification
        bar in the lower left corner?

        Use it to send your player request
        for help.

        The sucker is clearly be unable to deny you and will pay.

        <event:moveDialogueBoxDown>'
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Queen
      <Content>k__BackingField: Keep up the good work and don't win till you've filled
        your quota.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1063, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
